CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 22, 1958, pg. A9 reads: "AKA Tea - In preparation for their coming Debutante Cotillion, members of Alpha Kappa Alpha Sorority sponsored a mother-daughter tea last Sunday at the Spahr St. YWCA. Left to right are Delores Murphy, Mrs. Juanita Morris, Mrs. Eleanor McQueen, Ethel McQueen, Eileen Johnson, Patricia Morris and Mrs. Isabelle Johnson. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group of seven women, from left: Delores Murphy, Juanita Morris, Eleanor McQueen, Ethel McQueen, Eileen Johnson, Patricia Morris, and Isabelle Johnson, gathered for Alpha Kappa Alpha mother-daughter tea, Spahr Street YWCA.
